Responsibilities:

  Review and clarify test requirement
  Execute testing based on the test cases
  Perform the exploratory test and clarify test procedure when needed
  Perform troubleshooting and identify root causes for the issues and report the defects
  Record and document results
  Design and develop test cases based on the test requirements and specifications


Requirements:

  Minimum Diploma in Computer Science or relevant studies
  Minimum 1 year of software, hardware, network or prototype testing
  Experienced and skilled in Windows and/or Linux environment
  Able to work rotating shift (details will be discussed for shortlisted candidates)


Applicants who are more junior are welcome to apply.